research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0222.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family: topk\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_i \u03b1_i b_i\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d {b_i} \u6765\u81ea\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ea\u505a\u5355\u6837\u672c top-k \u9009\u62e9\u4e0e\u7cfb\u6570\u8ba1\u7b97\uff0c\u90e8\u7f72\u4fa7\u4ecd\u662f\u5355\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u57fa\u4e8e r218 \u5df2\u5728 total_cost=0.49x \u5904\u7ed9\u51fa\u5f53\u524d <0.5x \u533a\u57df\u6700\u4f73 FVU=0.1462\uff0c\u800c\u6700\u8fd1\u4e24\u8f6e\u66f4\u590d\u6742\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u7ed3\u6784 probe\uff08factorized_topk\u3001lowrank_factorized_residual@TRUNK_RANK=32\uff09\u5206\u522b\u7ed9\u51fa\u660e\u663e\u66f4\u5dee FVU\uff0c\u4e14 r221 \u8fd8\u628a\u541e\u5410\u538b\u5230 111k tokens/s\u3001\u603b\u65f6\u957f\u62c9\u5230 760s\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u66f4\u503c\u5f97\u5728\u6700\u5f3a\u4f4e\u5f00\u9500\u951a\u70b9\u4e0a\u505a\u4e0d\u589e\u52a0\u7cfb\u7edf\u6210\u672c\u7684\u5355\u53d8\u91cf recipe \u63a2\u9488\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u4e25\u683c\u951a\u5b9a r218\uff0c\u53ea\u6539 `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0`\uff0c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5728 EF=1\u3001K=248\u3001\u5b57\u5178\u5bb9\u91cf\u5df2\u5f88\u7d27\u3001\u652f\u6301\u96c6\u5df2\u5f88\u5927\u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c regime \u4e0b\uff0c\u53bb\u6389 auxiliary-K loss \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u51cf\u5c11\u5bf9\u4e3b\u91cd\u6784\u76ee\u6807\u7684\u5e72\u6270\uff0c\u5728\u4e0d\u6076\u5316 tokens_per_sec\u3001\u603b\u8017\u65f6\u548c final_total_tokens \u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u628a <0.5x \u524d\u6cbf FVU \u7ee7\u7eed\u538b\u4f4e\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0193.json:52:      "\u82e5 lowrank_residual \u660e\u663e\u52a3\u4e8e lowrank_soft_codebook_residual\uff0c\u5219\u4e0b\u4e00\u8f6e\u56de\u5230\u4e3b\u7ebf\uff0c\u53ea\u8c03\u4e00\u4e2a\u6210\u672c\u8f74\u5982 TRUNK_RANK\u3001NUM_CODES \u6216 STAGE1_RATIO\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0184.json:25:    "self_review": "本轮严格遵守单变量原则，只继续推进已经给出正面压缩信号的 `NUM_CODES` 轴；family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 全部保持不变。相比现在转去 `TRUNK_RANK` 或 optimizer，这一步更直接服务于 LUTurbo 总在线成本，因为它同时减少 coarse selector 成本和部署查表成本，并且能回答 coarse codebook 的最小可用规模这一尚未解决的问题。",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0184.json:61:      "若 `NUM_CODES=32` 明显退化，则说明 coarse branch 容量下限接近 64，下一轮回到 `NUM_CODES=64` 或 `128` 并改测 `TRUNK_RANK`。",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0184.json:83:    "self_review": "本轮严格遵守单变量原则，只继续推进已经给出正面压缩信号的 `NUM_CODES` 轴；family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 全部保持不变。相比现在转去 `TRUNK_RANK` 或 optimizer，这一步更直接服务于 LUTurbo 总在线成本，因为它同时减少 coarse selector 成本和部署查表成本，并且能回答 coarse codebook 的最小可用规模这一尚未解决的问题。",
research/history_archive/12_20260323_013532/round_summaries/round_0041.json:69:    "hypothesis": "`product_codebook_topk` did not fail on quality; it failed because the runtime still does not recognize the new architecture name. The next highest-value move is a narrow compatibility repair in the architecture validation/factory path so the discrete additive-codebook family can produce a real proxy signal before we decide whether to keep or archive this branch.",
research/history_archive/12_20260323_013532/round_summaries/round_0041.json:98:      "The blocker is registration/compatibility, not quality, so this round should be treated as infra repair rather than an architecture verdict.",
research/history_archive/12_20260323_013532/round_summaries/round_0041.json:104:      "If the repair exposes a second architecture-specific runtime issue, continue with one more narrow `code_fix` only if it is still local to `product_codebook_topk` registration or forward/backward compatibility."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0220.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r beta_r u_r + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {u_r} 是 trunk 静态向量库、{b_i} 是 residual 静态向量库；factorized residual scorer 只影响在线选择与系数计算，不改变 decoder 端导出形态，因此可直接落到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。基于 r210 已证明该 family 在 K=64、EF=1 下能以 0.69x 拿到 0.1256 FVU，当前主矛盾是 trunk 成本过高而不是训练质量不足；本轮严格锚定 r210，只改一个主轴 TRUNK_RANK，从 auto≈256 下调到 32，测试是否能把 total_cost 明确压入 <0.5x 区域，同时尽量保留明显优于同成本 topk 的 FVU。",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0220.json:20:    "summary": "相对 r210 的 lowrank_factorized_residual@K64,EF1 做一次严格 param_only 成本压缩，只下调 TRUNK_RANK 到 32，优先验证能否把该高质量 family 推入 total_cost < 0.5x 区域。",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0220.json:25:    "self_review": "该提案满足单变量原则：相对 r210 只改 TRUNK_RANK，其余核心配方保持不变。选择 32 而不是 16，是因为它仍应明显低于 0.5x，同时比更激进的 trunk 压缩更有机会保住 r210 展现出的质量优势；主要风险是 trunk 过窄后 coarse 补偿能力不足，FVU 可能回落到接近 topk。",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0220.json:49:        "key": "TRUNK_RANK",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0220.json:57:      "在 EF=1、K=64 下，TRUNK_RANK 是同时影响 encoder 与 deployment 的最高杠杆单变量；先压 trunk 比继续加 K 更符合当前 <0.5x 目标区。"
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0220.json:60:      "如果 TRUNK_RANK=32 仍明显优于 <0.5x 区域 topk 前沿，则继续相对本轮单变量下探 TRUNK_RANK=16，检查成本-质量拐点。",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0220.json:61:      "如果 TRUNK_RANK=32 的 FVU 退化过大，则保留 r210 作为质量锚点，转向同 family 的单变量 K 轴或回到 topk 前沿继续补点。"
