research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0220.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_factorized_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r beta_r u_r + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {u_r} 是 trunk 静态向量库、{b_i} 是 residual 静态向量库；factorized residual scorer 只影响在线选择与系数计算，不改变 decoder 端导出形态，因此可直接落到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。基于 r210 已证明该 family 在 K=64、EF=1 下能以 0.69x 拿到 0.1256 FVU，当前主矛盾是 trunk 成本过高而不是训练质量不足；本轮严格锚定 r210，只改一个主轴 TRUNK_RANK，从 auto≈256 下调到 32，测试是否能把 total_cost 明确压入 <0.5x 区域，同时尽量保留明显优于同成本 topk 的 FVU。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 TRUNK_RANK=32 仍明显优于 <0.5x 区域 topk 前沿，则继续相对本轮单变量下探 TRUNK_RANK=16，检查成本-质量拐点。","如果 TRUNK_RANK=32 的 FVU 退化过大，则保留 r210 作为质量锚点，转向同 family 的单变量 K 轴或回到 topk 前沿继续补点。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_factorized_residual 的导出形式稳定为 trunk 静态库 + residual 静态库的有限加权和，满足 LUTurbo 扩展兼容约束。","r210 的质量信号很强且训练吞吐约 166.6k tokens/s、总耗时 291s，说明该 family 值得优先做成本压缩而不是直接放弃。","在 EF=1、K=64 下，TRUNK_RANK 是同时影响 encoder 与 deployment 的最高杠杆单变量；先压 trunk 比继续加 K 更符合当前 <0.5x 目标区。"],"primary_variable":"other_param","reference_round":210,"self_review":"该提案满足单变量原则：相对 r210 只改 TRUNK_RANK，其余核心配方保持不变。选择 32 而不是 16，是因为它仍应明显低于 0.5x，同时比更激进的 trunk 压缩更有机会保住 r210 展现出的质量优势；主要风险是 trunk 过窄后 coarse 补偿能力不足，FVU 可能回落到接近 topk。","summary":"相对 r210 的 lowrank_factorized_residual@K64,EF1 做一次严格 param_only 成本压缩，只下调 TRUNK_RANK 到 32，优先验证能否把该高质量 family 推入 total_cost < 0.5x 区域。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0181.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_factorized_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_factorized_residual` under the unchanged mainline recipe (`K=128, EF=2, signum, lr=3.0e-3`). Final reconstruction is `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk and the residual coefficients are chosen by a factorized scorer but still decode as a finite weighted sum over a static residual dictionary `B`. This is `扩展兼容`: LUTurbo/Lottable can export the trunk factors and residual dictionary as static vector libraries, then run `trunk branch + factorized support scoring + weighted sparse lookup-sum` online. The single question is whether a lower-cost factorized residual selector is worth continuing versus the current two-stage soft-codebook mainline in the low-EF feasible regime. This probe should stay safely within the encoder-cost budget and gives a clean read on whether scorer factorization is a viable architecture direction rather than another likely policy reject.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["Return to the mainline `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round and tune exactly one cost knob such as `TRUNK_RANK`, `NUM_CODES`, or `STAGE1_RATIO`.","If `lowrank_factorized_residual` underperforms on FVU and/or slows throughput without a compensating cost advantage, mark factorized residual scoring as not worth continuing in the current low-cost regime."],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_factorized_residual` is LUTurbo `扩展兼容`: the factorized encoder changes selector-side scoring only; decode remains a finite weighted sum over static trunk and residual libraries.","This matched probe tests a still-compatible low-cost architecture direction that has not recently been revisited under the current `K=128, EF=2, signum, lr=3e-3` regime.","Review `tokens_per_sec`, wall-clock time, and `final_total_tokens` together with FVU; if factorization only saves selector cost proxy but trains materially slower or reconstructs worse, treat that as a negative signal."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"Single-variable discipline is preserved: only `ARCHITECTURE` changes while `K`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, `OPTIMIZER`, and `LR` remain fixed to the mainline recipe. This probe stays inside the compatible and likely feasible set, and it answers a distinct architectural question about whether factorized scoring is intrinsically worth keeping alive on the Pareto search path.","summary":"Probe `lowrank_factorized_residual` as the one matched architecture change. It is LUTurbo-exportable (`扩展兼容`) through a static low-rank trunk plus static residual dictionary, and it tests whether factorized residual scoring is worth continuing against the current soft-codebook two-stage mainline in the low-EF feasible regime.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0180.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_residual_vq"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"lowrank_residual_vq","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_residual_vq` under the unchanged mainline recipe (`K=128, EF=2, signum, lr=3.0e-3`). Final reconstruction is `x_hat = U(Vx) + c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk library, `c_m` is one selected codebook vector from a static coarse library, and the residual term is a weighted sum over a static residual dictionary. This is `扩展兼容` because LUTurbo/Lottable can export the trunk factors, coarse codebook, and residual dictionary as static vector libraries, then run `trunk branch + coarse code lookup + sparse residual lookups + weighted sum` online. The single question for this probe is whether replacing the soft coarse branch with a hard VQ-style coarse branch is worth continuing in the low-EF feasible regime. This should stay inside the encoder-cost budget at `EF=2`, so it is likely to produce a real training/runtime signal rather than another policy reject.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["Return to the mainline `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round and tune exactly one cost knob such as `TRUNK_RANK`, `NUM_CODES`, or `STAGE1_RATIO`.","If `lowrank_residual_vq` underperforms the mainline on FVU or slows training without a compensating runtime/quality benefit, mark hard-VQ coarse branches as not worth continuing in the current low-cost regime."],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_residual_vq` is LUTurbo `扩展兼容`: decode is a finite weighted sum over static trunk vectors, one static coarse codebook entry, and static residual dictionary atoms.","This matched probe tests a meaningful architecture axis that has not been revisited recently in the current low-EF regime: soft coarse branch versus hard coarse branch.","Review `tokens_per_sec`, total runtime, and `final_total_tokens` alongside FVU; a small quality change with worse throughput should count against continuing the family."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"Single-variable discipline is preserved: only `ARCHITECTURE` changes while `K`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, `OPTIMIZER`, and `LR` remain fixed to the mainline recipe. This probe stays within the compatible family set, is likely budget-feasible, and answers a clean architectural question without drifting into another over-budget selector variant.","summary":"Probe `lowrank_residual_vq` as the one matched architecture change. It is LUTurbo-exportable (`扩展兼容`) through a static low-rank trunk, a static coarse codebook, and a static residual dictionary, and it tests whether a hard coarse branch is worth continuing versus the current soft-codebook two-stage mainline.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0133.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"pareto_cost_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态可导出的固定向量库，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。当前 family 在 EF=2 时已满足 selection_cost ≤ 1.5×h×n，本轮不再继续无收益的 LR/loss 试探，而只改一个部署相关主变量：将 TRUNK_RANK 下调到 32，测试是否能在进一步降低 encoder selection_cost 与 trunk/codebook deploy 成本的同时，把 FVU 保持在接近当前 0.0581 的水平，从而形成新的 cost-FVU Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 TRUNK_RANK=32 能明显降成本且 FVU 仅小幅退化，可继续细扫更低或中间 rank 以压出新的 Pareto 前沿。","若 TRUNK_RANK=32 的 FVU 明显恶化，则说明当前 trunk 容量已接近下限，后续应回到默认 rank 并改测 NUM_CODES。","若 TRUNK_RANK=32 与 baseline 几乎等价且吞吐更好，则可将更低 rank 视为新的 clean baseline，再继续 recipe 搜索。"],"notes_to_memory":["LUTurbo 导出形式未变，family 仍为扩展兼容。","EF=2 继续保证选择成本在硬约束内；本轮通过降低 TRUNK_RANK 探索更低成本 Pareto，而不是追求单点最优 FVU。","r132 表明 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 与 baseline 基本等价，因此暂时结束 loss 轴试探，转向更有系统价值的成本轴。"],"primary_variable":"trunk_rank","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 均固定，只改 TRUNK_RANK。该动作直接服务于 LUTurbo 的真实目标，因为它同时触碰 encoder 选择成本与部署 trunk 成本；风险是 trunk 容量下降可能导致 coarse branch 表达不足，因此必须结合 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和最终 token 数一起判断是否值得保留。","summary":"在低成本可行主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 上做一次成本轴探索：固定 EF=2、K=128、signum、LR=3.0e-3，仅把 TRUNK_RANK 下调到 32，判断能否以更低 selection/deploy 成本维持接近当前 frontier 的重构质量。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0183.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"NUM_CODES","value":"64"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 low-rank trunk 库 U、静态 soft codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都可静态导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。r182 在只把 NUM_CODES 从默认 256 降到 128 时，FVU 与整条训练曲线都基本不变，说明当前 coarse codebook 仍有明显冗余。本轮只回答一个问题：把 NUM_CODES 继续降到 64，是否仍能基本保持主线质量，同时进一步降低 code_router、codebook_matmul 与 codebook_deploy 的总成本，从而改善 LUTurbo 可部署 Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 NUM_CODES=64 仍接近 0.0581 且吞吐/总耗时不恶化，则继续沿 codebook size 轴下探，或把 64 作为新的低成本 clean mainline。","若 NUM_CODES=64 出现明显 FVU 退化，则说明 128 已接近 coarse branch 下限，下一轮回到 NUM_CODES=128 并改测 TRUNK_RANK。","若 FVU 基本不变但 tokens_per_sec 再次异常下滑，则优先把该现象视为运行时噪声信号，而不是结构负面结论。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 在 `NUM_CODES=64` 下导出路径不变，仍是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + two-stage residual 字典库的有限加权和。","r182 已表明 `NUM_CODES=128` 相对 baseline 几乎零质量损失，因此继续缩小 codebook 是当前最干净的单变量成本推进。","评估本轮必须同时检查 curve_start/mid/end、tokens_per_sec、总耗时、final_total_tokens，确认收益来自真实成本下降而非运行时漂移。"],"primary_variable":"other_param","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 全部固定，只继续沿 `NUM_CODES` 这一主成本旋钮推进。相比重复测过的 TRUNK_RANK，这一步更直接触碰 coarse branch 的选择成本和部署查表成本，且与 r182 形成自然的连续主线。","summary":"继续主线 family，不开新架构；固定 `K=128, EF=2, signum, LR=3.0e-3`，仅把 `NUM_CODES` 从 128 再降到 64，验证 coarse codebook 是否还能继续压缩而不明显伤害 FVU，从而进一步降低 LUTurbo 的总在线成本。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0158.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"该 family 的最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 U(Vx) 可离线导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终重构仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r157 已在当前低 EF 主线下再次给出 adam 的爆炸性负信号，因此 optimizer 分支可视为已被明确关闭。按推荐顺序，下一步应转向 loss/preprocess 轴；本轮只回答一个问题：在保持 family、EF、K、主优化器和 LR 不变的前提下，完全去掉 auxiliary K loss（AUXK_ALPHA=0.0）是否能减少对主重构目标的干扰，带来更好的曲线形状或至少确认该辅助项在当前可部署 regime 下已无必要。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 在不恶化吞吐与总时长的前提下改善曲线或终点，则下一轮做一次同配方 clean repeat 确认。","若 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 与基线几乎等价，则记录 auxiliary loss 在该 regime 下非关键，随后再考虑更贴近系统成本的 K 轴。","若 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 明显退化，则恢复默认辅助项并结束 loss 轴试探。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 继续满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","EF=2 下 selection_cost 仍在预算内；本轮不改 EF、K、TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或其他成本轴，只隔离 auxiliary loss 效应。","r157 在当前主线 regime 下再次复现了 adam 的强负信号，optimizer 分支应正式关闭。","评估本轮必须同时记录 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，区分是否存在由训练更长或吞吐异常造成的假信号。"],"primary_variable":"auxk_alpha","self_review":"这轮严格只改一个主变量 AUXK_ALPHA，family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 全部固定，符合单变量原则。当前策略顺序在 optimizer 之后本就应转向 loss/preprocess，而 r157 已把 optimizer 问题回答得足够清楚；因此继续停留在 optimizer 分支价值很低，不如用最小改动检查辅助损失在当前低成本主线中的必要性。","summary":"继续围绕主线 family 推进，不开新 family；在 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum、LR=3.0e-3 固定的前提下，仅将 AUXK_ALPHA 设为 0.0，判断去掉 auxiliary K loss 是否能改善当前可部署 regime 的训练曲线或确认其已无必要。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0112.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.4e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j；其中 low-rank trunk、soft codebook、两阶段 residual 都是静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，因此该 family 属于扩展兼容。单主变量改为 EXPANSION_FACTOR: 12 -> 2，可把该 family 的 selection_cost 压到约 1.16x h×n，回到 ≤1.5x 硬预算内，同时保留当前主线结构，回答“这个强 backbone 在最低可行 EF 下是否仍能以更低总在线成本给出比 factorized_topk 更好的 FVU/时延权衡”。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 EF=2 已可行且 FVU 仍明显优于 factorized_topk，则下一轮在同 family 上补 clean baseline，检查曲线是否仍在下降。","若 EF=2 曲线形状健康但收敛偏慢，则只调 LR 作为单变量。","若 EF=2 的 FVU 退化过大，则保留该 family 但转向单变量降低 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM 或 TRUNK_RANK，探索 EF=2 下更便宜 scorer 的最优点。"],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性：扩展兼容；导出形式为 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。","本轮严格遵守单变量原则，只验证 EF 收缩后的成本可行性与低 EF 表达质量。","K 对选择成本几乎无影响，因此保持 K=128，不把成本变化和稀疏预算变化混在一起。"],"primary_variable":"expansion_factor","self_review":"这是当前策略要求下最小且可归因的主线动作：先把主线 family 拉回预算内，再看其低 EF regime 是否仍有竞争力。风险是 EF=2 可能让 FVU 明显恶化，但这正是本轮唯一要回答的问题。","summary":"继续主线 family，不开新架构。用参考配方 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual / K=128 / signum / LR=2.4e-3，仅将 EXPANSION_FACTOR 从 12 降到 2，先验证该扩展兼容结构在 LUTurbo 选择成本预算内的可行 Pareto 点。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0177.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"routed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"routed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `routed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` under the unchanged mainline recipe (`K=128, EF=2, signum, lr=3.0e-3`). Final reconstruction remains `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j`; routing only perturbs stage-1/stage-2 support selection scores, while all decoded terms still come from static trunk, codebook, and residual libraries. This is `扩展兼容` because LUTurbo/Lottable can export the low-rank trunk matrices, soft codebook vectors, and residual dictionary once, then execute `trunk lookup + codebook lookup + routed support selection + weighted sparse lookups + sum` online. The key question is whether router-driven support allocation is worth continuing in the low-EF feasible regime. Current cost accounting strongly suggests no: adding two full routers likely pushes encoder selection cost above the `1.5x h×n` hard cap, so the most informative outcome is a quick policy gate that rules this family out as a mainline candidate at `EF=2`.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["Return to the mainline `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round and tune exactly one cost knob such as `TRUNK_RANK`, `NUM_CODES`, or `STAGE1_RATIO`.","If this routed matched probe is policy-rejected as expected, mark routed two-stage soft-codebook as not worth continuing in the current low-cost regime unless a future single-variable cost-reduction round explicitly targets router cost."],"notes_to_memory":["`routed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` is LUTurbo `扩展兼容`: routing changes selector logic only; decode path is still a finite weighted sum over static trunk/codebook/residual libraries.","At matched `K=128, EF=2`, routed two-stage soft-codebook is expected to exceed the encoder-cost cap because the two router projections add substantial full-dictionary selection cost on top of the mainline scorer.","Treat a fast policy rejection here as a useful architectural conclusion, not a runtime failure: the family is exportable but not cost-viable in the current feasible regime."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"Single-variable discipline is preserved: only `ARCHITECTURE` changes, while `K`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, `OPTIMIZER`, and `LR` remain fixed to the mainline recipe. This probe is intentionally chosen to answer a clean architectural question under the new budget regime: whether routing is inherently worth carrying forward once low-EF cost feasibility is enforced.","summary":"Probe `routed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` as the one matched architecture change. It is LUTurbo-exportable (`扩展兼容`) by the same static-library decomposition as the mainline, but is likely to be ruled out quickly because the extra routers make encoder selection cost exceed the hard budget, which would mean this family is not worth continuing on the current Pareto frontier.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0222.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，部署侧仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。基于 r218 已在 total_cost=0.49x 处给出当前 <0.5x 区域最佳 FVU=0.1462，而最近两轮更复杂低成本结构 probe（factorized_topk、lowrank_factorized_residual@TRUNK_RANK=32）分别给出明显更差 FVU，且 r221 还把吞吐压到 111k tokens/s、总时长拉到 760s，说明当前更值得在最强低开销锚点上做不增加系统成本的单变量 recipe 探针。本轮严格锚定 r218，只改 `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0`，测试在 EF=1、K=248、字典容量已很紧、支持集已很大的低成本 regime 下，去掉 auxiliary-K loss 是否能减少对主重构目标的干扰，在不恶化 tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens 的前提下，把 <0.5x 前沿 FVU 继续压低。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 在保持接近 r218 吞吐与总时长的同时把 FVU 压到 0.1462 以下，则下一轮对该无辅助损失配方做一次 clean repeat 确认，再考虑继续围绕 topk 低成本主线做 recipe 局部化。","如果 `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 与 r218 基本等价，则记录 auxiliary loss 在 `topk@EF1,K248` 低成本主线中不是关键因子，随后转向同一锚点上的单变量 LR probe。","如果 `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 明显退化，则恢复默认 auxiliary loss，并将 loss 轴在该 low-cost topk 主线上暂时关闭。"],"notes_to_memory":["r221 证明低秩 trunk 压缩在 lowrank_factorized_residual 上同时伤害质量与运行代价，不应继续占用 <0.5x 主线轮次。","当前最有价值的动作是在已知最强 <0.5x 点 `topk@EF1,K248` 上做不改变部署成本的单变量 recipe probe，而不是继续引入更长选择链路。","若 `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 成功，则说明在高 K、低 EF 的单库 topk 低成本 regime 中，auxiliary K loss 可能只是训练干扰项而非必要正则。"],"reference_round":218,"self_review":"该提案满足单变量原则：相对有效参考轮 r218 只改 `AUXK_ALPHA`，不改 family、K、EF、optimizer、LR 或其他结构参数。相比继续做新的 architecture probe，这一步信息更干净，因为它直接回答当前最强 <0.5x 锚点是否还有零部署增量的可挖掘训练收益；风险是 auxiliary loss 可能仍对活跃特征利用有帮助，但这正是本轮要隔离验证的问题。","summary":"相对 r218 的 `topk@EF1,K248` 做一次严格 param_only loss 轴验证，仅将 `AUXK_ALPHA` 设为 0.0，判断去掉 auxiliary-K loss 能否在不增加系统成本和运行时负担的前提下继续压低 <0.5x 前沿 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0186.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"16"}],"expected_win":"pareto_improve","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j；其中 low-rank trunk 库 U、静态 soft-codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都可静态导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。当前 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 仍满足 ≤1.5×h×n 硬约束。r133 把 `TRUNK_RANK` 降到 32 时几乎零损失复现了主线 FVU，r182-r184 继续压缩 `NUM_CODES` 也未改变终点，说明当前主线可能仍有明显结构冗余。本轮只回答一个问题：将 `TRUNK_RANK` 进一步下调到 16，是否仍能保持接近当前主线的训练曲线与终点 FVU，同时继续降低 trunk 相关的 encoder 选择成本与部署查表成本，从而推动兼容 Pareto 前沿向更低总成本移动。","summary":"继续围绕同一主线 family 推进，不开新 family；固定 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, K=128, EF=2, OPTIMIZER=signum, LR=3.0e-3`，仅把 `TRUNK_RANK` 从已验证无损的 32 再降到 16，测试更激进的 trunk 压缩是否仍能维持当前 LUTurbo 可部署质量。","needs_sanity":false,"notes_to_memory":["family 与导出路径不变，`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 在 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 下仍是扩展兼容：trunk 库 + soft-codebook 库 + two-stage residual 字典库的有限加权和。","r133 表明 `TRUNK_RANK=32` 相对主线几乎无损，因此继续沿 trunk 容量轴下探比重复未增益的 `NUM_CODES` 压缩更有信息价值。","评估本轮必须同时比较 curve_start/mid/end、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，确认任何收益来自真实成本下降而非运行时漂移。"],"next_hypotheses":["若 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 仍接近当前主线 FVU 且吞吐不恶化，可将更低 rank 视为新的低成本主线，并考虑继续下探或做一次 clean baseline 复验。","若 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 明显退化，则说明 trunk 容量下限更接近 32，下一轮回到 `TRUNK_RANK=32` 并转向 `NUM_CODES` 或其他单一成本轴。","若终点接近但吞吐显著变差，则把更低 trunk rank 视为负面系统信号，而不是仅凭 FVU 保留。"],"primary_variable":"trunk_rank","self_review":"本轮严格遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 全部固定，只推进 `TRUNK_RANK` 这一直接作用于 encoder 选择成本和部署 trunk 成本的主变量。相比继续尝试在 policy 上有风险的 optimizer 分支，这一步更稳、更可归因，也更贴近 LUTurbo 的真实总成本目标。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0116.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.6e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk、soft codebook、两阶段 residual 都可静态导出为固定向量库上的有限加权和，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；该 family 属于扩展兼容。Round 114 和 Round 115 已确认在 EF=2、K=128、signum 下，`LR=3.0e-3` 可稳定复现当前可行 frontier 点 `FVU≈0.0581`，且 encoder 选择成本仍在 1.5x 预算内。本轮只改一个主变量 `lr`，向上小步探测到 `3.6e-3`，回答唯一问题：在不改变成本与部署形态的前提下，更积极的 signum 步长能否继续改善曲线和终点 FVU，还是已经越过稳定收敛区间。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `LR=3.6e-3` 进一步改善终点或早中期下降，且 `tokens_per_sec`、总耗时、`final_total_tokens` 没有明显恶化，则把更高 LR 作为新的主线候选并考虑一次复现确认。","如果 `LR=3.6e-3` 出现震荡、回退，或只带来极小 FVU 收益却显著拖慢训练，则关闭向上 LR 分支，保留 `LR=3.0e-3` 为 EF=2 主线锚点。","在 LR 轴结论明确前，不切换 optimizer，不改 K，也不改 TRUNK_RANK / NUM_CODES / STAGE1_RATIO / FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM。"],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性判断：`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 为扩展兼容；导出形式仍是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。","EF=2 已稳定满足 encoder 选择成本硬约束，当前可行 frontier 点为 `sel≈1.25x, deploy≈0.62x, FVU≈0.05811`。","本轮严格单变量，只改 `lr`；评估时必须同时检查曲线形状、`tokens_per_sec`、总耗时与 `final_total_tokens`，避免为微小 FVU 收益付出不成比例的训练代价。"],"primary_variable":"lr","self_review":"这符合当前主线顺序：EF 已确认在预算内，clean baseline 已补齐并复现，下一步应继续完成 LR 局部化，再考虑 optimizer。选择 `3.6e-3` 是对已验证有效的 `3.0e-3` 做单步上探，仍然只改一个主变量，归因清晰。","summary":"在已确认成本可行且可复现的 `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` EF=2 主线上，仅将 `LR` 从 `3.0e-3` 上调到 `3.6e-3`，测试更高 signum 步长是否还能继续改善低成本 Pareto 点。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0157.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"该 family 的最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 U(Vx) 可离线导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终重构仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下的 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r153-r155 已先后补齐 clean baseline 并把 signum 的 LR 曲线看清，3.3e-3 虽有小幅稳定收益，但当前策略顺序要求在 LR 之后先回答 optimizer 问题，且 r156 的 K 轴尝试已被 policy 拦截，因此本轮只改一个主变量 OPTIMIZER：保持 family、EF、K、LR 与导出形式不变，仅将优化器从 signum 切到 adam，回答唯一问题：在同样的可部署低成本 regime 下，optimizer 本身是否仍有值得保留的曲线形状或终点信号，还是应被再次明确关闭。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 adam 在相同 LR=3.0e-3 下再次明显爆炸或曲线极差，则正式关闭该 family 在当前低 EF regime 的 optimizer 分支，后续不再用它驱动主线。","若 adam 没有爆炸且曲线具备可比性，即使终点未赢，也可记录为需要一次 optimizer-local LR callback 的候选。","若 adam 意外优于 signum 基线，则下一轮再严格做一次单变量的 optimizer 分支确认或回调。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 继续满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","EF=2 下 selection_cost 仍在预算内；本轮不改 EF、K、TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或其他成本轴，只隔离 optimizer 效应。","r153-r155 已把主线 baseline 与 LR 曲线重新看清；当前最缺的是在现行策略顺序下对 optimizer 的明确结论。","评估时必须同时记录 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，区分是优化器本身导致训练更慢、更长，还是直接数值不稳定。"],"primary_variable":"optimizer","self_review":"这轮严格只改一个主变量 optimizer，family、EF、K、LR 全部固定，符合单变量原则和当前主线推进顺序。虽然历史上 adam 在该 family 上已有负信号，但在当前回合策略明确要求 LR 之后先看 optimizer，而 r156 的 K 轴尝试已被 policy 拦截；因此最合规且信息量最高的动作是用当前参考配方再给 optimizer 一次干净结论，而不是继续提前动 K。","summary":"继续围绕主线 family 推进，不开新 family；固定 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、LR=3.0e-3，仅将 OPTIMIZER 从 signum 切到 adam，判断 optimizer 分支在当前可部署 regime 下是否仍值得保留。","touched_files":[]}
