research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0212.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_factorized_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r beta_r u_r + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {u_r} 是静态 trunk 向量库、{b_i} 是静态 residual 向量库；factorized scorer 只影响在线选择与系数计算，不改变 decoder 端的静态库有限加权和形式，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性为扩展兼容。单主变量选择 TRUNK_RANK：在保持 ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_factorized_residual、K=64、EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3 不变时，把 trunk_rank 从当前 auto≈128 下调到 32，测试当前 0.69x 点的主要冗余是否来自过大的 trunk 库；若 trunk 只是提供粗补偿而 residual 分支已承担主要表达，则可把 encoder+deployment 总成本一口气压入 <0.5x 区域，同时维持明显优于 topk@0.31x 的 FVU。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 TRUNK_RANK=32 仍保持明显优于 topk@EF1,K64 的 FVU 且进入 <0.5x，则固定该 family 后只沿 K 轴做一次补点。","如果 TRUNK_RANK=32 的 FVU 退化过大，则说明该 family 的收益高度依赖 trunk 容量，低开销主战场应回到更短链路的 topk 或新的轻量单库方案。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_factorized_residual 的导出形式稳定为 trunk 静态库 + residual 静态库的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容，可继续保留在兼容 frontier 候选集中。","r210 在 0.69x 处取得 0.1256 FVU，且 tokens_per_sec≈166.6k、总耗时 291s，明显快于近期 topk/soft-codebook 线；因此优先压缩 trunk_rank 比继续增大 K 更符合当前低开销与训练成本双目标。"],"primary_variable":"other_param","self_review":"这轮只改一个主轴 TRUNK_RANK，归因干净，且直接针对 r210 暴露出的成本结构问题。选择 32 而不是 64，是因为 64 大概率仍停留在 >0.5x 边界外；32 才有机会真正补上当前最缺的 <0.5x 前沿，但风险是 trunk 过度压缩后 FVU 可能明显反弹。","summary":"在扩展兼容的 lowrank_factorized_residual 上做一次低开销 param-only 探索：固定 K=64、EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，仅把 TRUNK_RANK 压到 32，目标是在保留 trunk+residual 双库导出形式的同时，把当前 0.69x 候选推进到 <0.5x 区域。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0119.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk、soft codebook、两阶段 residual 都是静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；该 family 属于扩展兼容。当前 EF=2 已稳定满足 encoder 选择成本硬约束，`signum + LR=3.0e-3` 是已复现的低成本主线锚点；将 `AUXK_ALPHA` 从 0.03125 降到 0.015625 后未见明显退化，说明辅助稀疏损失在该低 EF regime 里可能已非必要。本轮只改一个主变量 `AUXK_ALPHA`，进一步降到 `0.0`，回答唯一问题：完全去掉 auxiliary K loss 是否能减少对主重构目标的约束干扰，在不增加训练代价的前提下进一步改善 FVU 或曲线形状。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 改善终点或曲线形状，且 `tokens_per_sec`、总耗时、`final_total_tokens` 基本不变，则再做一次 clean baseline 复现确认。","如果 `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 出现退化，则关闭 auxk 降低分支，恢复默认 `0.03125` 或保留已验证等价的较小值，不再继续在该轴上消耗轮次。","在 loss/preprocess 轴未得到清晰正信号前，不改 K，也不改 TRUNK_RANK / NUM_CODES / STAGE1_RATIO / FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM。"],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性判断：`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 为扩展兼容；导出形式不变，仍是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。","`adam` 分支已爆炸，当前主线仍应固定在 `signum + LR=3.0e-3`。","本轮严格单变量，只改 `AUXK_ALPHA`；该改动不影响 encoder 选择成本，也不应显著增加训练时长，评估时继续同时检查曲线形状、`tokens_per_sec`、总耗时与 `final_total_tokens`。"],"primary_variable":"auxk_alpha","self_review":"这仍符合当前主线顺序。EF、clean baseline、LR 和 optimizer 结论都已基本清楚，而上轮把 `AUXK_ALPHA` 减半后没有负面信号，因此现在最小且可归因的后续问题就是测试 auxiliary loss 是否可以彻底移除。相比切换到更重的 preprocess 改动，这个问题更干净、代价更低。","summary":"保持 `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual / EF=2 / K=128 / signum / LR=3.0e-3` 主线不变，仅将 `AUXK_ALPHA` 进一步降到 `0.0`，测试低成本 regime 下是否可以完全去掉 auxiliary K loss 来改善重构质量。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0193.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i；其中 low-rank trunk 项 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库上的加权和，residual 分支 Σ_i alpha_i b_i 可导出为静态 residual 字典上的稀疏加权和，因此能够落到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’推理链路，兼容性为扩展兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，去掉 soft codebook coarse branch 后，lowrank_residual 是否仍值得作为更低 encoder selection cost 的极简兼容支线；若 FVU 相比主线与 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 都明显恶化，则说明 coarse codebook 分支本身是当前主线不可缺少的结构增益。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 lowrank_residual 明显劣于 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，则下一轮回到主线，只调一个成本轴如 TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或 STAGE1_RATIO。","若 lowrank_residual 在更低 selection_cost 下仍保持可接受 FVU 且训练更快，可将其保留为更低成本的兼容备选支线。","继续避免 routed 与 bucketed matched probe，因为它们在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 超过 1.5×h×n 预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","lowrank_residual 的导出路径是 trunk 静态库 + residual 静态字典库的有限加权和，属扩展兼容。","r192 已确认 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 以 0.75x selection cost 获得 0.06466 FVU；本轮进一步测试去掉 coarse codebook 后，soft codebook 分支本身是否值得其额外成本。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这是一个比 r192 更激进的父节点回退 probe，但仍严格满足 matched architecture-only 约束，并且科学问题单一明确：隔离 soft codebook coarse branch 的结构价值。该 family 已在 frontier 上有可行点，成本更低但 FVU 更差，因而这轮主要是确认它是否仍值得保留，而不是期望取代主线。","summary":"执行一个 matched architecture probe：将主线切到 lowrank_residual，其余 recipe 保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。该架构的最终重构为 trunk 静态库与 residual 静态字典上的有限加权和，属扩展兼容；本轮只回答一个问题，即在 LUTurbo 成本约束下，去掉 soft codebook coarse branch 的更低成本父节点是否还值得继续保留。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0187.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"8"}],"expected_win":"pareto_improve","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j；其中 low-rank trunk 库 U、静态 soft-codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都可静态导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。当前 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 仍满足 ≤1.5×h×n 硬约束。r133 的 `TRUNK_RANK=32` 与 r186 的 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 都未伤害终点 FVU，说明 trunk 容量可能仍有可压缩冗余。本轮只回答一个问题：将 `TRUNK_RANK` 进一步下调到 8，是否仍能保持接近当前主线的训练曲线与终点 FVU，同时继续降低 trunk 相关的 encoder 选择成本与部署查表成本，从而把兼容 Pareto 点继续推向更低总成本。","summary":"继续围绕同一主线 family 推进，不开新 family；固定 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, K=128, EF=2, OPTIMIZER=signum, LR=3.0e-3`，仅把 `TRUNK_RANK` 从 16 再降到 8，测试更激进的 trunk 压缩是否仍能维持当前 LUTurbo 可部署质量。","needs_sanity":false,"notes_to_memory":["family 与导出路径不变，`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 在 `TRUNK_RANK=8` 下仍是扩展兼容：trunk 库 + soft-codebook 库 + two-stage residual 字典库的有限加权和。","`TRUNK_RANK=32` 与 `16` 都复现了约 0.0581 FVU，因此继续沿 trunk 容量轴下探比回到已多次无增益的 codebook 轴更有信息价值。","评估本轮必须同时比较 curve_start/mid/end、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，确认收益来自真实成本下降而不是运行时漂移。"],"next_hypotheses":["若 `TRUNK_RANK=8` 仍接近当前主线 FVU 且吞吐不恶化，可将更低 rank 视为新的低成本主线，并考虑一次 clean baseline 复验来确认曲线稳定性。","若 `TRUNK_RANK=8` 明显退化，则说明 trunk 容量下限更接近 16，下一轮回到 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 并转向 `NUM_CODES` 或其他单一成本轴。","若终点接近但吞吐显著变差，则把更低 trunk rank 视为负面系统信号，而不是仅凭 FVU 保留。"],"primary_variable":"trunk_rank","self_review":"本轮严格遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 全部固定，只推进 `TRUNK_RANK` 这一直接作用于 encoder 选择成本和部署 trunk 成本的主变量。相比现在切回高风险的 optimizer 分支，这一步更稳、更可归因，也更贴近 LUTurbo 的真实总成本目标。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0191.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i；其中 low-rank trunk U(Vx)、soft codebook 库 {c_m} 与 residual 字典 {b_i} 都可静态导出到 LUTurbo 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’链路，因此该 family 属于扩展兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，去掉第二阶段 residual refinement 后，lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 仍可能以更低的 encoder 选择成本与更快训练吞吐保住一个有价值的 Pareto 点；若 FVU 明显回退，则说明 stage-2 是当前主线真正有效的结构增益。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若该 probe 的 FVU 仍显著落后于 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual，则下一轮回到主线，只调一个成本轴如 TRUNK_RANK / NUM_CODES / STAGE1_RATIO。","若该 probe 以更低 selection_cost 保持接近 FVU 且训练更快，可把 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 重新视为低成本支线继续做单轴 recipe 清洗。","继续避免 routed / bucketed matched probe at EF=2，因为其 selection_cost 约 2.25x h×n，已超 policy 预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外显式保持 K=128、EF=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 为扩展兼容，导出路径是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。","在 EF=2 下，lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 的 selection_cost 约 0.75x h×n，低于主线 two-stage 的 1.25x；routed / bucketed 同配方约 2.25x，当前不可行。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这不是全新 family，信息增益低于真正新结构；但在当前 matched、兼容、且满足成本约束的候选里，它是最干净的 probe。最近的 grouped/gated/asymmetric siblings 已给出负信号，而 routed/bucketed 在 EF=2 被预算拦截，因此本轮用 one-stage parent 来隔离‘第二阶段 residual 是否值得其额外成本’是最可解释的动作。","summary":"执行一个 matched architecture probe：把主线从 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 切到其 one-stage 父节点 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，其余 recipe 保持 K=128 / EF=2 / signum / LR=3.0e-3 不变。该 family 的 LUTurbo 导出公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，属扩展兼容；本轮重点看去掉 stage-2 后，是否能用更低 encoder 选择成本与更快训练代价维持一个值得保留的 Pareto 点。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0117.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk、soft codebook、两阶段 residual 都可静态导出为固定向量库上的有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；该 family 属于扩展兼容。当前主线在 EF=2 下已稳定满足 encoder 选择成本硬约束，且 signum 的 LR 轴已基本收敛：`LR=3.0e-3` 两轮复现优于 `2.4e-3`，而 `3.6e-3` 回退到 `FVU=0.058151...`，说明继续上探学习率的价值已下降。本轮只改一个主变量 `optimizer`，把 `OPTIMIZER` 从 `signum` 切到 `adam`，其余保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, K=128, EXPANSION_FACTOR=2, LR=3.0e-3` 不变，回答唯一问题：在同样成本与部署形态下，adam 是否能带来更好的低成本 Pareto 点或更优曲线形状。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `adam` 在 `LR=3.0e-3` 下曲线健康且终点接近或优于 `signum`，则给 `adam` 一次单变量 LR 回调机会。","如果 `adam` 明显更差、发散或运行代价明显恶化，则关闭 optimizer 分支，保留 `signum + LR=3.0e-3` 为 EF=2 主线锚点。","在 optimizer 问题解决前，不改 K，也不改 TRUNK_RANK / NUM_CODES / STAGE1_RATIO / FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM。"],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性判断：`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 为扩展兼容；导出形式仍是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。","LR 轴结论：`LR=3.0e-3` 是当前更稳的 signum 主线候选；`LR=3.6e-3` 未带来改进，因此应停止继续上探。","本轮严格单变量，只改 `optimizer`；评估时继续同时检查曲线形状、`tokens_per_sec`、总耗时与 `final_total_tokens`，避免用更高训练代价换取不显著收益。"],"primary_variable":"optimizer","self_review":"这符合当前主线顺序：EF 已确认在预算内，clean baseline 已补齐，LR 轴也已通过 `3.0e-3` 与 `3.6e-3` 的结果基本收束，下一步应进入 optimizer 分支。保持 LR、EF、K 不变，只改 `optimizer`，归因清晰，并且遵守单变量原则。","summary":"停止继续上探 signum 学习率，转而在同一低成本主线配方上仅将 `OPTIMIZER` 从 `signum` 切到 `adam`，测试是否能在 EF=2 的可部署 regime 下得到更好的曲线或终点 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0196.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i；其中 {b_i} 是单个静态字典库中的固定向量，alpha_i 是由低秩 factorized scorer 在线选择得到的稀疏系数。factorized scorer 只改变选择路径，不改变 decoder 端的单库有限加权和形式，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’推理链路，兼容性为直接兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，factorized_topk 是否能以更低 encoder selection cost（约 0.38x h×n）保留足够可用的 FVU；若其相对 topk 仍无实用优势，则说明单库 factorized selector 在当前低 EF regime 下也不值得继续占用主线注意力。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 factorized_topk 仍明显劣于 lowrank_residual / lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，则下一轮回到主线，只调一个成本轴如 TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或 STAGE1_RATIO。","若 factorized_topk 相比 topk 以更低选择成本获得更好或接近的 FVU 且训练更快，可将其保留为最便宜的直接兼容 selector 支线。","继续避免 routed 与 bucketed matched probe，因为它们在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 超过 1.5×h×n 预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","factorized_topk 的导出路径是单一静态字典库上的有限稀疏加权和，属直接兼容。","r195 已确认 plain topk 在当前 regime 下 FVU=0.1755 且被 discard；本轮进一步验证更低成本的 factorized selector 是否值得保留。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这是一个严格单变量的 matched probe，科学问题清晰：最便宜的直接兼容 factorized 单库架构是否还有 LUTurbo 价值。它不改变部署公式，只隔离 selector 低秩化本身的效果，适合在连续多轮 probe 后给单库路线一个更完整的结论。","summary":"执行一个 matched architecture probe：将主线切到 factorized_topk，其余 recipe 保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。该架构的最终重构是单一静态字典库上的有限稀疏加权和，属直接兼容；本轮只回答一个问题，即低秩 factorized selector 是否足以让最便宜的单库 LUTurbo 方案继续值得保留。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0175.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"bucketed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"bucketed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `bucketed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` under the mainline recipe (`K=128, EF=2, signum, lr=3e-3`). Final reconstruction is `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j`, where the bucket gate only changes stage-1/2 selector scores and all decoded terms still come from static libraries `{U,V}`, codebook `C`, and residual dictionary `B`. This is `扩展兼容` with a clean LUTurbo export path, but the matched EF=2 selector is likely not worth continuing because bucketed dual scorers raise encoder selection cost to about `2.5x h×n`, so the policy should reject it before spending a long training run.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["Return to the mainline `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round and tune one cost knob at a time (`TRUNK_RANK`, `NUM_CODES`, or `STAGE1_RATIO`) to improve the feasible Pareto point without changing architecture.","If a future bucketed revisit is desired, only do it as a cost-reduction study on the bucketed family itself with primary variable `TRUNK_RANK` or `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`, not as another matched-architecture probe."],"notes_to_memory":["`bucketed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` is LUTurbo `扩展兼容`: bucket mixing changes selector-side scoring only; decode remains a finite weighted sum over static trunk/codebook/residual libraries.","At matched `K=128, EF=2`, the bucketed two-stage soft-codebook family estimates to about `selection_cost=2.5x` and is therefore over the `1.5x` hard budget; this makes it a likely fast policy-reject probe rather than a training candidate."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"Single-variable discipline is preserved: architecture is the only changed dimension, while `K/EF/optimizer/LR` are pinned to the mainline recipe. I am choosing an intentionally decisive probe: it is informative even if rejected, because the low-EF budget constraint is now the main gate and this family is known to be runtime-heavier. This does not claim the family is universally bad; it only answers whether it is worth continuing on the current feasible low-cost frontier.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe on `bucketed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` with the mainline recipe unchanged otherwise. The family is LUTurbo-exportable (`扩展兼容`) via a static trunk library plus static codebook and residual dictionaries, but its matched EF=2 selector cost is expected to exceed budget (`~2.5x h×n`), so the likely result is a cheap policy rejection that cleanly answers: this architecture is not worth continuing as a low-cost mainline candidate right now.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0126.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"lower_selection_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j，其中 U(Vx) 对应可静态导出的 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，最终仍可落到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’推理链路，因此兼容性为扩展兼容。当前主线已确认 EF=2 在预算内，而 signum/LR/K 轴最近几轮没有带来改进，本轮只回答一个问题：在保持 family、K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变的前提下，下调 TRUNK_RANK 到 32，能否进一步压低 encoder 选择成本并维持可接受的 FVU，从而得到更优的 Pareto 权衡。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 TRUNK_RANK=32 仅小幅伤害 FVU 但明显降低 selection_cost，则继续沿 trunk_rank 轴补一个中间点以细化 Pareto。","若 TRUNK_RANK=32 明显恶化 FVU 且时间收益有限，则恢复默认 trunk 配方，转向 loss/preprocess 轴。","若 TRUNK_RANK=32 同时改善时间与 selection_cost，但 FVU 退化可接受，则把它作为低成本分支保留，不再继续降 K。"],"notes_to_memory":["family 不变，兼容性仍为扩展兼容，导出路径不变：trunk 库 + soft-codebook 库 + residual 字典库。","r125 复现了 K=96 的较差 FVU，说明继续压 K 的回报有限，本轮改测更直接作用于 encoder 成本的 trunk_rank。","评估时必须同时记录 selection_cost、FVU、总耗时、tokens_per_sec、final_total_tokens，区分收益来自真实算子简化还是训练时长波动。"],"primary_variable":"trunk_rank","self_review":"本轮严格只改一个主变量，并把探索重心从已基本洗净的 signum/LR/K 轴转向更贴近 Pareto 目标的 selection-cost 轴。风险在于 TRUNK_RANK=32 可能过于激进，但它能最快回答该 family 是否还有内部压缩空间。","summary":"保持 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 主线与 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变，仅下调 TRUNK_RANK 到 32，测试是否能以有限 FVU 损失换取更低 encoder 成本和更好的 LUTurbo 总体权衡。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0178.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_gated_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"lowrank_gated_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_gated_residual` under the unchanged mainline recipe (`K=128, EF=2, signum, lr=3.0e-3`). Final reconstruction is `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk library and the gated selector only changes which residual dictionary atoms `b_i` are activated and with what coefficients. This is `扩展兼容`: LUTurbo/Lottable can export the trunk factors and residual dictionary as static vector libraries, then run `trunk branch + gated sparse selection + weighted lookup-sum` online. The architectural question is whether dropping the soft-codebook branch but using a gated residual selector yields a better low-cost tradeoff than the current two-stage soft-codebook mainline. Selection cost should remain within the feasible regime at `EF=2`, so this probe should produce a real training signal rather than another fast policy reject.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["Return to the mainline `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round and tune exactly one cost knob such as `TRUNK_RANK`, `NUM_CODES`, or `STAGE1_RATIO`.","If `lowrank_gated_residual` trails the mainline on FVU and/or slows tokens_per_sec without a compensating benefit, mark the family as not worth continuing in the low-EF feasible regime."],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_gated_residual` is LUTurbo `扩展兼容`: decode is still a finite weighted sum over a static low-rank trunk plus a static residual dictionary; gating only affects selector-side scoring.","This is a useful matched probe because it is likely budget-feasible at `EF=2`, unlike routed/bucketed two-stage variants, and it tests whether the soft-codebook branch is actually necessary in the current low-cost regime.","When evaluating the run, inspect `tokens_per_sec`, wall-clock time, and `final_total_tokens` alongside FVU; a small FVU gain with materially worse throughput should count as a negative signal."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"Single-variable discipline is preserved: only `ARCHITECTURE` changes, with `K`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, `OPTIMIZER`, and `LR` fixed to the mainline recipe. This probe is intentionally chosen to answer a clean architectural question inside the feasible cost band instead of spending another round on an architecture that is likely to be policy-rejected immediately.","summary":"Probe `lowrank_gated_residual` as the one matched architecture change. It is LUTurbo-exportable (`扩展兼容`) through a static low-rank trunk plus static residual dictionary, and it should give a real low-EF signal about whether gated residual selection is worth continuing once the soft-codebook branch is removed.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0184.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"NUM_CODES","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"pareto_improve","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式仍为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j；其中 low-rank trunk 库 U、静态 soft-codebook 库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都可静态导出，因此可映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。r182 与 r183 在连续下调 `NUM_CODES` 后仍复现约 0.0581 FVU，说明 coarse codebook 可能还有可压缩冗余。本轮只回答一个问题：将 `NUM_CODES` 进一步下调到 32，是否仍能维持接近当前主线的训练曲线与终点 FVU，同时继续降低 `code_router`、`codebook_matmul` 与 `codebook_deploy` 成本，从而把当前主线点向更低总成本方向推进。","summary":"继续围绕当前主线 family 推进，不开新 family；固定 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, K=128, EF=2, OPTIMIZER=signum, LR=3.0e-3`，仅把 `NUM_CODES` 从 64 再降到 32，测试 coarse codebook 是否还能继续压缩而不明显伤害 LUTurbo 可部署质量。","expected_win_reason":"If `NUM_CODES=32` still preserves the curve shape and endpoint, it improves the compatible Pareto point by cutting coarse-branch selection and deployment cost without changing the export formula.","needs_sanity":false,"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 在 `NUM_CODES=32` 下导出路径不变，仍是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + two-stage residual 字典库的有限加权和，因此保持扩展兼容。","r183 若在 `NUM_CODES=64` 下仍复现约 0.0581 FVU，则 coarse codebook 冗余尚未耗尽，继续沿 `NUM_CODES` 轴下探比切换到新 recipe 更符合单变量主线推进。","评估本轮必须同时比较 curve_start/mid/end、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，区分是真实结构退化还是近期运行时吞吐波动。"],"next_hypotheses":["若 `NUM_CODES=32` 仍接近当前主线 FVU 且运行代价未显著恶化，可将更小 codebook 视为新的低成本主线并考虑继续下探或回到 clean baseline 复验。","若 `NUM_CODES=32` 明显退化，则说明 coarse branch 容量下限接近 64，下一轮回到 `NUM_CODES=64` 或 `128` 并改测 `TRUNK_RANK`。","若 FVU 基本不变但吞吐再次异常波动，则优先视为运行时噪声，避免把吞吐抖动误判成结构结论。"],"primary_variable":"num_codes","self_review":"本轮严格遵守单变量原则，只继续推进已经给出正面压缩信号的 `NUM_CODES` 轴；family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 全部保持不变。相比现在转去 `TRUNK_RANK` 或 optimizer，这一步更直接服务于 LUTurbo 总在线成本，因为它同时减少 coarse selector 成本和部署查表成本，并且能回答 coarse codebook 的最小可用规模这一尚未解决的问题。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0192.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i；其中 low-rank trunk 项 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库上的加权和，soft codebook 分支 Σ_m pi_m c_m 可导出为静态 codebook 库上的加权和，residual 分支 Σ_i alpha_i b_i 可导出为静态 residual 字典上的稀疏加权和，因此能够映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’推理链路，兼容性为扩展兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的条件下，lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 以更低 encoder selection cost（frontier 已显示约 0.75x vs 主线 1.25x）有望提供值得保留的 cost/FVU 点；若其 FVU 明显落后，则说明 two-stage refinement 本身值得继续保留。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若该 probe 明显劣于主线，则下一轮回到 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual，只调一个成本轴如 TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或 STAGE1_RATIO。","若该 probe 在更低 selection_cost 下接近主线且训练更快，可把 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 作为低成本支线继续做单轴清洗。","继续避免 routed 与 bucketed matched probe，因为在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 约 2.25x h×n，会被预算约束卡住。"],"notes_to_memory":["r191 的 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 提案被 policy_reject，原因是用 param_only 承载架构切换；同一假设应以 architecture 类型重提。","本轮严格 matched：只改 architecture，其余保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3。","该 family 为扩展兼容，导出路径是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这是对 r191 被 policy 拦截的同一科学问题做合法重提，不引入第二主变量。相比继续试 grouped/gated/asymmetric 的兄弟结构，one-stage parent 能更直接回答 two-stage 增益是否值得其额外选择成本；同时它已在当前 frontier 上显示为可行兼容点，信息增益和可解释性都足够。","summary":"执行一个合法的 matched architecture probe：将主线从 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 切到 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，其余 recipe 保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。该架构的最终重构可导出为 trunk 静态库、soft codebook 静态库和 residual 静态字典上的有限加权和，属扩展兼容；本轮只回答一个问题，即去掉第二阶段 residual refinement 后，这个 family 是否仍值得继续保留为低成本 LUTurbo 候选。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0137.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态可导出的固定向量库，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。最近 r132/r133/r136 在改 AUXK_ALPHA、TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 后得到几乎完全相同的 start/mid/end FVU、tokens_per_sec 与 final_total_tokens，说明当前更需要先补一轮无附加成本轴扰动的 clean baseline，确认主线 reference recipe 的真实曲线与运行代价，再决定下一轮是向上还是向下微调 LR。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 clean baseline 仍复现 0.0581 且晚段仍在改善，则下一轮只下调 LR 到 2.4e-3，测试是否能改善末段收敛。","若 clean baseline 的曲线比近期 archive 更差或更快平台化，则下一轮只上调 LR 到 3.6e-3，测试当前 3.0e-3 是否偏保守。","若 clean baseline 与近期三轮继续完全重合，则说明 recipe 已高度稳定，后续应优先做单变量 LR 扫描而不是继续扫成本侧小参数。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的导出形式未变，仍属扩展兼容，可继续作为 LUTurbo 主线 family。","r132/r133/r136 的 FVU 曲线与吞吐几乎完全一致，近期成本轴小改动没有提供新的可解释信号。","本轮先补 clean baseline，是为了恢复后续 LR 试验的可靠参照，而不是扩大搜索空间。"],"primary_variable":"other_param","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 固定到当前主线参考配方，不引入新的结构改动，也不混入额外 recipe 变量。该动作不追求立刻刷新 FVU，而是先建立可信的 clean baseline，避免在近期多轮零信号的情况下继续做难归因的参数扰动。风险是这一轮可能再次得到与近期相同的结果，但即便如此也能为下一轮 LR 单变量搜索提供干净参照。","summary":"继续主线 family，不开新架构；在已确认 EF=2 成本可行后，先补一轮 exact clean baseline：lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, K=128, EF=2, signum, LR=3.0e-3，无额外成本侧或 loss 侧改动。目标是确认当前主线配方的真实训练曲线、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，再据此进入单变量 LR 调整。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0176.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` under the unchanged mainline recipe (`K=128, EF=2, signum, lr=3e-3`). Final reconstruction is `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j`, with the only architectural change versus the mainline being a fixed front-loaded sparse budget split (`stage1_k≈0.75K`, `stage2_k≈0.25K`). This is `扩展兼容` because LUTurbo can export the low-rank trunk, soft codebook, and residual dictionary as static libraries and execute them in the usual `trunk lookup + codebook lookup + two residual lookups + weighted sum` pipeline. Because this family keeps the same trunk/codebook/residual components as the mainline and only reallocates K across the two residual stages, its encoder selection cost should remain within the same feasible regime as the current mainline rather than triggering policy rejection. The probe answers one question only: at low-cost EF=2, is front-loading the residual budget intrinsically better than the symmetric two-stage split, or should this family be deprioritized.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["Return to the mainline `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round and tune a single cost knob such as `TRUNK_RANK`, `NUM_CODES`, or `STAGE1_RATIO`.","If the asymmetric probe underperforms or slows training without clear FVU benefit, mark the family as not worth continuing in the low-EF feasible regime."],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` is LUTurbo `扩展兼容`: export path is identical to the mainline soft-codebook two-stage family; only stage budget allocation changes.","This is the cleanest remaining matched architecture probe because it preserves the mainline's static libraries and likely feasible encoder cost, avoiding another likely policy-reject like routed/bucketed variants.","When reviewing the run, check not just FVU but also `tokens_per_sec`, total runtime, and `final_total_tokens` to see whether any gain is offset by slower training."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"Single-variable discipline is preserved: only `ARCHITECTURE` changes, while `K`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, `OPTIMIZER`, and `LR` stay fixed. I am avoiding another clearly over-budget probe and choosing a matched variant that isolates one architectural question while remaining compatible with LUTurbo export and likely feasible under the selection-cost constraint.","summary":"Probe `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` as the one matched architecture change against the current mainline recipe. It is LUTurbo-exportable (`扩展兼容`), keeps the same static trunk/codebook/residual libraries, and tests whether a front-loaded two-stage residual budget is worth continuing in the low-EF feasible regime.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0221.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r u_r + Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {u_r} 是静态 trunk 向量库、{b_i} 是静态 residual 向量库；在线侧只计算 β_r 与 α_i，再执行 trunk 查表 + residual 查表 + 加权求和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。r220 的 blocker 不是质量，而是 TRUNK_RANK override 没有真正进入训练配置；当前执行链已具备 `TRUNK_RANK -> --trunk_rank -> sae.trunk_rank` 路径，因此本轮应严格锚定有效参考轮 r210，只改一个 env 参数 `TRUNK_RANK=32`，先验证 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 都记录 `sae.trunk_rank=32`，再判断该 family 是否能以预估 total_cost≈0.36x 保持显著优于 <0.5x 区域 topk 前沿的 FVU，同时保住其更高吞吐/更短总时长。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果配置审计通过且 `TRUNK_RANK=32` 仍明显优于 `topk@0.38x` 的 FVU=0.1968，并且吞吐接近 r210 的 166.6k tokens/s，则下一轮继续相对本轮单变量下探 `TRUNK_RANK=16`，寻找更低成本拐点。","如果配置审计通过但 `TRUNK_RANK=32` 的 FVU 退化过大，则仍保留这轮作为有效成本点，下一轮在同 family 内回退到更温和的 `TRUNK_RANK=64` 做单变量 bracket，而不是立即切去新 family。","如果这轮再次出现 `TRUNK_RANK` 未进入 runtime/checkpoint config，则停止解读任何 FVU，直接转入接线修复验证轮。"],"notes_to_memory":["r220 无效的根因是参数接线而非架构质量；下一轮必须把“参数确实进入 runtime_config 与 checkpoint config”作为第一判据。","本地 `selection_cost_estimate()` 显示 `lowrank_factorized_residual@K64,EF1,TRUNK_RANK=32` 的 combined_ratio 约为 0.36x，显著低于 r210 的 0.69x，也低于当前 `topk@K248,EF1` 的 0.49x。","若该点质量接近 r210 的 FVU=0.1256，同时维持其约 166.6k tokens/s、291s 级别的训练代价，则会成为 <0.5x 区域比 topk 更强的高价值 Pareto 点。"],"reference_round":210,"self_review":"这轮继续遵守单变量原则：相对有效 reference r210 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`，不重复把 `ARCHITECTURE/K/EF/LR` 写进 patch，也不使用已经被审计标记无效的 r220 作为锚点。选择复跑 `TRUNK_RANK=32` 而不是直接去 `16`，是因为当前最高优先级是先消除变量隔离失效这个 blocker，并拿到第一条真实有效的低 trunk-rank 证据；在审计通过之前，不应把结果当成架构结论。","summary":"复跑 r220 的科学问题，但按合法 `param_only` 形式严格锚定有效参考轮 r210，仅下发 `TRUNK_RANK=32`。本轮先做参数生效确认，再评估 lowrank_factorized_residual 是否能以约 0.36x total_cost 进入 <0.5x Pareto 主前沿。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0182.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"NUM_CODES","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"pareto_improve","experiment_tier":"mainline","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"active","hypothesis":"Mainline cost-reduction step on `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` with only `NUM_CODES` changed from the implicit default to `128`. Final reconstruction remains `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j`, so this family is still `扩展兼容`: LUTurbo/Lottable can export the low-rank trunk library, the static codebook library `C`, and the static residual dictionary `B`, then run `trunk lookup + codebook lookup + two sparse residual lookups + weighted sum` online. This round asks one question only: can a smaller coarse codebook preserve most of the EF=2 mainline quality while reducing both encoder selection cost and deployment lookup cost enough to improve the Pareto point. Reducing `NUM_CODES` directly shrinks `code_router`, `codebook_matmul`, and `codebook_deploy`, making it a cleaner first cost knob than changing multiple recipe terms at once.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["If `NUM_CODES=128` holds FVU close to the current mainline while reducing cost, continue along the same axis with a smaller codebook or then test `TRUNK_RANK` as the next single cost knob.","If FVU degrades sharply, revert to the current mainline codebook size and try `TRUNK_RANK` instead as the next mainline cost-reduction variable."],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` remains LUTurbo `扩展兼容` under `NUM_CODES=128`; only the size of the static coarse codebook changes, not the export path.","This round isolates the coarse-codebook-size question and should reduce both selection cost and deployment cost simultaneously, unlike `STAGE1_RATIO` which mostly reallocates sparse budget without shrinking static lookup structures.","Review `tokens_per_sec`, wall-clock time, and `final_total_tokens` together with FVU to confirm whether any improvement comes from true efficiency rather than a shorter or cheaper run artifact."],"primary_variable":"num_codes","self_review":"Single-variable discipline is preserved: the family and main recipe stay fixed, and only `NUM_CODES` changes. This follows the stated mainline priority order by keeping EF in-budget and then applying a direct cost knob that can improve both selector cost and LUTurbo deployment cost without introducing a new architecture.","summary":"Push the mainline family forward by shrinking the coarse codebook to `NUM_CODES=128` while keeping `K=128`, `EF=2`, `signum`, and `lr=3e-3` fixed. This is a clean Pareto test for whether the current two-stage soft-codebook architecture can trade a smaller static coarse library for lower total LUTurbo cost without giving up too much reconstruction quality.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0156.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"112"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.3e-3"}],"expected_win":"smaller_k","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"该 family 的最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 low-rank trunk 库 U、soft-codebook 静态库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 静态字典库 {b_i} 都可离线导出，因此最终仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接落到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。当前 EF=2 下该 family 的 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，仍满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束，而 r154-r155 已把 signum 主线 LR 稳定到 3.3e-3。既然 optimizer 分支在 EF=2、同 family 上已出现爆炸性负信号，loss 轴与 TRUNK_RANK=32 也未带来收益，本轮只回答一个更贴近 LUTurbo 总在线成本的问题：在保持 family、EF、optimizer、LR 不变时，仅将 K 从 128 小步下调到 112，能否在明显降低部署查表成本的同时，把 FVU 维持在接近当前 0.05794 的水平，从而形成更优的总成本权衡点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 K=112 仅小幅退化且部署成本改善明显，则继续沿 K 轴小步下探到 104 或 96。","若 K=112 已明显恶化到接近先前 K=96 的趋势，则关闭降 K 分支，保留 K=128 作为该 family 的主线部署点。","若 K=112 几乎不损失 FVU，则将更小 K 升格为新的主线配方，并再评估其曲线与吞吐稳定性。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 继续满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","EF=2 下 selection_cost 仍在预算内；本轮改 K 不触碰 encoder 成本硬约束，只改变部署查表成本。","r154-r155 已把 signum@3.3e-3 复验为稳定优于 3.0e-3 的主线 LR。","adam 在该 family/EF=2 上已有爆炸性负信号，AUXK_ALPHA 与 TRUNK_RANK=32 也未显示有效收益；因此当前更高价值的问题是更贴近系统目标的 K 轴成本权衡。","评估本轮必须同时记录 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，确认收益不是由异常训练时长或吞吐波动伪造。"],"primary_variable":"k","self_review":"这轮严格只改一个主变量 K，符合单变量原则，也仍留在当前主线 family。虽然策略顺序通常先看 optimizer，但该分支在同一低 EF regime 已给出强负信号；继续重复低价值 optimizer 试探不如转向更贴近 LUTurbo 总在线成本目标的部署查表成本轴。选择 112 而不是直接回到 96，是为了做更小、更可归因的降 K 台阶，避免一次性损失过多表示能力。","summary":"继续围绕主线 family 推进，不开新 family；固定 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、signum、LR=3.3e-3，仅将 K 从 128 小步下调到 112，测试是否能以更低部署查表成本维持接近当前最佳的 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0210.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_factorized_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r beta_r u_r + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 u_r 是静态 trunk 向量库，b_i 是静态 residual 向量库；在线侧只计算系数 beta_r 与 alpha_i，并在 LUTurbo/Lottable 端导出为两个静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此属于扩展兼容。r209 对 topk@EF1,K96 的继续加大查表预算被 policy 拦截，说明单纯沿 topk 的 K 轴上探不稳；本轮保持 K=64、EF=1、optimizer、LR 不变，只把 architecture 从 topk 切到 lowrank_factorized_residual，测试在仍瞄准 <0.5x 区域的前提下，加入极轻 low-rank trunk 与 factorized residual scorer 后，是否能显著优于 topk@0.31x 的 FVU。按现有成本表外推，该配置有希望落在低开销区或其边界附近，同时提供比纯单库 topk 更强的表达。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 lowrank_factorized_residual@EF1,K64 成功落入 <0.5x 且明显优于 topk@EF1,K64，则下一步固定该 family，单变量扫描 K 或 TRUNK_RANK，补齐低开销前沿。","如果该配置仍超出 <0.5x 或 FVU 改善有限，则说明低开销区需要更短链路而非增加 trunk 分支，下一步应回到 topk/factorized_topk 或探索更小静态库方案。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_factorized_residual 的导出形式是 trunk 静态库加 residual 静态库的有限加权和，满足 LUTurbo 扩展兼容约束。","本轮只改 architecture，保持 K=64 和 EF=1 不变，便于判断在同等低字典规模与相近 lookup 预算下，增加轻 trunk 是否值得。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"该提案遵守单变量原则，并直接回应 r209 的 policy_reject：不再继续沿 topk 的 K 轴加预算，而是测试更有信息量的新低成本 family。主要风险是 deployment 侧 trunk 成本可能把 total_cost 推到 0.5x 附近甚至略上，但这仍能为低开销区提供关键边界信号。","summary":"切换到扩展兼容的 lowrank_factorized_residual，固定 K=64、EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，只改变 architecture，验证轻量 trunk+residual 结构能否在低开销区附近拿到明显优于 topk 的 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0213.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"16"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r beta_r u_r + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {u_r} 是静态 trunk 向量库，{b_i} 是静态 residual 向量库；在线侧只计算系数 beta_r 与 alpha_i，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时可拆成 trunk 库查表加权和与 residual 库查表加权和，两部分都满足静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此兼容性为扩展兼容。基于 r210 已在当前 family 上拿到 0.69x / 0.1256 且 tokens_per_sec 约 166.6k、总耗时 291s，当前最值得回答的单一问题不是再换 family，而是该点的高成本是否主要由 trunk 过宽导致；本轮仅将 TRUNK_RANK 下调到 16，测试能否在保持明显优于 topk@0.31x 的 FVU 前提下，把 total_cost 尽量压向并最好压入 <0.5x 区域。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 TRUNK_RANK=16 进入 <0.5x 且 FVU 仍明显优于 topk@EF1,K64，则固定该 family 后只沿 K 轴补一个点。","如果 TRUNK_RANK=16 的 FVU 明显崩塌或训练代价没有进一步优势，则说明 lowrank_factorized_residual 在低开销区仍过度依赖 trunk 容量，后续应回到更短链路 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["r210 说明 lowrank_factorized_residual 在低 EF 下具备很强质量潜力，且运行吞吐优于近期 topk 线；当前主要矛盾是成本而非训练不稳。","TRUNK_RANK 同时影响 encoder 与 deployment 两侧成本，是把该 family 从 0.69x 拉回低开销区的最高信息量单变量旋钮。"],"primary_variable":"trunk_rank","self_review":"这轮严格只改一个主变量 trunk_rank，不再重复声明 K、EF、optimizer、LR，避免再次触发 param_only 的多主轴拒绝。选择 16 而不是 32，是因为目标是优先补 <0.5x 区域覆盖；更激进地下压 trunk 才更可能一次性把该高质量点推进到低开销前沿，但风险是 coarse trunk 表达会被过度削弱。","summary":"在扩展兼容的 lowrank_factorized_residual 上做一次低开销 param-only 探索：仅将 TRUNK_RANK 设为 16，验证能否以更小 trunk 库把当前 0.69x/0.1256 的高质量点推进到 <0.5x 区域。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0179.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_jumprelu_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"lowrank_jumprelu_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` under the unchanged mainline recipe (`K=128, EF=2, signum, lr=3.0e-3`). Final reconstruction is `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk and the JumpReLU selector only changes which residual dictionary atoms `b_i` are activated and their coefficients. This is `扩展兼容`: LUTurbo/Lottable can export the trunk factors and residual dictionary as static vector libraries, then execute `trunk lookup + thresholded sparse selection + weighted lookup-sum` online. The probe asks one question only: in the low-EF feasible regime, does learned thresholding provide a better architecture tradeoff than the current soft-codebook two-stage mainline, or should this family be ruled out. Encoder selection cost should stay in the feasible band at `EF=2`, so this should produce a real signal instead of a policy reject.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["Return to the mainline `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round and tune exactly one cost knob such as `TRUNK_RANK`, `NUM_CODES`, or `STAGE1_RATIO`.","If `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` underperforms the mainline on FVU or shows materially worse `tokens_per_sec`/runtime without compensating benefit, mark the family as not worth continuing in the low-cost regime."],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_jumprelu_residual` is LUTurbo `扩展兼容`: decode remains a finite weighted sum over a static low-rank trunk plus a static residual dictionary; JumpReLU only changes selector-side activation sparsity.","This matched probe stays inside the likely feasible encoder-cost regime and is more informative than another routed/bucketed-style over-budget probe.","When scoring the run, inspect `tokens_per_sec`, wall-clock time, and `final_total_tokens` together with FVU; a tiny quality gain with slower training is a negative signal."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"Single-variable discipline is preserved: only `ARCHITECTURE` changes while `K`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, `OPTIMIZER`, and `LR` remain fixed to the mainline recipe. This probe avoids another likely budget rejection and tests a remaining compatible architecture that can still deliver a clean go/no-go answer for the low-EF frontier.","summary":"Probe `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` as the one matched architecture change. It is LUTurbo-exportable (`扩展兼容`) through a static low-rank trunk plus static residual dictionary, and it should give a real low-cost signal on whether learned thresholding is worth continuing versus the current soft-codebook two-stage mainline.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0132.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态可导出的固定向量库，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。由于 r131 的 optimizer 分支被 policy_reject，先停止继续扫 optimizer；本轮只回答一个问题：在主线 baseline（signum, LR=3.0e-3）上去掉 auxiliary K loss（AUXK_ALPHA=0.0）后，是否能改善训练末段收敛形状并在不增加选择成本、不过度拖慢 tokens_per_sec/总耗时的前提下降低 FVU。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 曲线更平滑且终点更好，可继续围绕 aux loss 强度做单变量细扫。","若 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 终点变差或训练早期明显失稳，则说明 auxiliary 信号仍有价值，回到 baseline 后再考虑 preprocess 轴。","若 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 与 baseline 几乎等价，则结束 loss 轴试探，后续再评估更细的部署成本变量如 TRUNK_RANK 或 NUM_CODES。"],"notes_to_memory":["LUTurbo 导出形式未变，family 仍为扩展兼容；本轮不引入新 family。","EF=2 继续满足 selection_cost 预算；K 保持 128，避免把部署查表成本变化与 loss 轴混杂。","r131 optimizer 分支被 policy_reject，因此本轮转向更保守的 loss 轴单变量试探，而不是继续扩张 optimizer 搜索。"],"primary_variable":"auxk_alpha","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、主优化器和 LR 都固定，只改 AUXK_ALPHA。该提案避开了刚被 policy 拒绝的 optimizer 分支，继续在兼容且成本可行的主线 family 上获取可解释信号；风险是 auxiliary loss 关闭后可能导致早期 support 学习变差，因此必须结合曲线形状与运行代价共同判断。","summary":"在已稳定复现的 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 主线上做一次 loss 轴最小改动：固定 EF=2、K=128、signum、LR=3.0e-3，仅关闭 auxiliary K loss，判断该辅助项是否在当前低 EF 可行区间内已经成为收敛噪声。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0194.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i；其中 low-rank trunk 项 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库上的加权和，residual 分支 Σ_i alpha_i b_i 可导出为静态 residual 字典上的稀疏加权和。factorized scorer 只改变在线选择打分路径，不改变最终 decoder 形式，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’推理链路，兼容性为扩展兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，lowrank_factorized_residual 是否能以更低 encoder selection cost（约 0.5x h×n）提供一个仍值得保留的低成本支线；若 FVU 明显劣于 lowrank_residual，则说明 factorized scorer 在当前低 EF regime 下损失过大，不值得继续作为主线兼容方向。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 lowrank_factorized_residual 明显劣于 lowrank_residual，则下一轮回到主线，只调一个成本轴如 TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或 STAGE1_RATIO。","若它在显著更低 selection_cost 下维持可接受 FVU 且训练更快，可将 factorized scorer 保留为低成本 selector 方向。","继续避免 routed 与 bucketed matched probe，因为它们在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 超过 1.5×h×n 预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","lowrank_factorized_residual 的导出路径仍是 trunk 静态库 + residual 静态字典库的有限加权和，属扩展兼容。","r193 已确认 plain lowrank_residual 在 0.62x selection cost 下 FVU=0.0730；本轮进一步隔离 factorized scorer 是否值得用额外误差换更低选择成本。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这是一个严格单变量的 matched probe，科学问题单一明确：验证 factorized scorer 这类低成本选择机制在兼容 residual family 中是否值得继续。虽然其现有 frontier 点较弱，但它能直接回答‘更便宜的 selector 是否还能保住可用 FVU’这一部署相关问题，信息价值高于重复已失败的 soft-codebook siblings。","summary":"执行一个 matched architecture probe：将主线切到 lowrank_factorized_residual，其余 recipe 保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。该架构的最终重构仍是 trunk 静态库与 residual 静态字典上的有限加权和，属扩展兼容；本轮只回答一个问题，即 factorized scorer 带来的更低 encoder 成本是否足以让该 family 继续作为 LUTurbo 低成本候选。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0197.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i；其中 {b_i} 是单个静态字典库中的固定向量，alpha_i 是经 gate 调制后的在线稀疏系数。gate 只改变选择与系数计算路径，不改变 decoder 端的单库有限加权和形式，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性为直接兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，gated 是否能在仍满足选择成本预算（EF=2 下约 1.0x h×n）的情况下，相比 topk 提供更好的 FVU；若它仍明显落后于 lowrank_residual / lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，则说明纯单库 gated 路线在当前低 EF regime 下也不值得继续。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 gated 仍明显劣于 lowrank_residual / lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，则下一轮回到主线，只调一个成本轴如 TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或 STAGE1_RATIO。","若 gated 相比 topk 有稳定收益但仍远逊于 low-rank family，可将 gate 只视为 selector-side 局部技巧，而非主线候选。","继续避免 routed 与 bucketed matched probe，因为它们在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 超过 1.5×h×n 预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","gated 的导出路径是单一静态字典库上的有限稀疏加权和，属直接兼容。","r195 topk 已在当前 regime 下被 discard，r196 factorized_topk 更弱；本轮补完直接兼容单库路线中 gate 调制是否值得保留。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这是一个严格单变量的 matched probe，问题明确：单库 gated 是否比 plain/factorized topk 更有保留价值。它不改变部署形式，只检查 gating 这一 selector 机制本身；在当前已经基本排空更便宜单库路线后，这个 probe 能给直接兼容路线更完整的结论。","summary":"执行一个 matched architecture probe：将主线切到 gated，其余 recipe 保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。该架构的最终重构是单一静态字典库上的有限稀疏加权和，属直接兼容；本轮只回答一个问题，即单库 gated selector 是否足以让该 family 继续作为 LUTurbo 低成本候选。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0185.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j；其中 low-rank trunk 库 U、静态 soft-codebook 库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都可静态导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。当前主线在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 仍在 1.5×h×n 硬约束内，且连续 3 轮围绕 `NUM_CODES` 压缩都没有改变曲线终点，说明当前瓶颈更可能在优化动态而不是 coarse codebook 容量。本轮只回答一个问题：把主变量切到 `optimizer`，并使用更保守的 `adam@1.0e-3`，是否能在不改变 family/EF/K 的前提下改善训练曲线形状或终点 FVU，而不是继续在 signum 配方周围得到同样的 plateau。","summary":"停止继续细扫 `NUM_CODES`，回到同一主线 family 的 recipe 轴；固定 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, K=128, EF=2`，将主变量切到 `optimizer`，测试 `adam` 配合更保守的 `LR=1.0e-3` 是否能打破当前 signum 主线的收敛平台。","needs_sanity":false,"notes_to_memory":["family 与导出路径不变，`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 仍是扩展兼容：trunk 库 + soft-codebook 库 + two-stage residual 字典库。","连续 3 轮 `NUM_CODES` 压缩没有改变终点 FVU，说明当前主线更值得优先澄清 optimizer/curve-shape 问题，而不是继续沿 coarse codebook 容量轴下探。","评估本轮必须同时比较 curve_start/mid/end、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，判断收益是否来自更优优化动态，而不是更长训练或运行时波动。"],"next_hypotheses":["若 `adam@1.0e-3` 曲线更平滑且终点优于或接近 signum 主线，则给 adam 一次同轴 LR callback，例如 `1.5e-3`。","若 `adam@1.0e-3` 明显更差或更慢，则关闭 optimizer 分支，恢复 signum 主线，并回到 `TRUNK_RANK` 或 `NUM_CODES` 的成本轴。","若终点接近但吞吐明显更差，则将 adam 视为负面系统信号，即使其数值指标不差。"],"primary_variable":"optimizer","self_review":"本轮保持同一 family，不开新架构，并把问题从已经反复无增益的 codebook 容量轴转回 recipe 轴，符合当前“先把同一 family 的训练曲线看清”的要求。虽然 `optimizer` 轴联动了更保守的 `LR=1.0e-3`，但这属于避免用 signum 学习率误判 adam 的必要局部配套；主问题仍然只有一个：当前平台是否主要来自优化器动态。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0195.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i；其中 {b_i} 是单个静态字典库中的固定向量，alpha_i 是每个样本在线选择得到的稀疏系数，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’推理链路，兼容性为直接兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，最朴素的 topk 单库架构是否仍值得作为极低部署成本、低选择成本的 LUTurbo 备选；若其 FVU 相比 lowrank_residual / lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 明显恶化，则说明 low-rank trunk 与 coarse branch 不是锦上添花，而是当前可用性的必要结构。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 topk 明显劣于 lowrank_residual，则下一轮回到主线，只调一个成本轴如 TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或 STAGE1_RATIO。","若 topk 以更低部署成本和更快训练吞吐表现出可接受 FVU，可将其保留为最简直接兼容基线支线。","继续避免 routed 与 bucketed matched probe，因为它们在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 超过 1.5×h×n 预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","topk 的导出路径是单一静态字典库上的有限稀疏加权和，属直接兼容。","r192-r194 已逐步验证去掉 stage2、去掉 soft codebook、再改成 factorized scorer 都会带来明显 FVU 损失；本轮进一步测试去掉 low-rank trunk 后，最简单单库家族是否还有保留价值。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这是一个严格单变量的 matched probe，问题单一明确：最简直接兼容单库架构在当前低 EF regime 下是否还有 LUTurbo 价值。它不追求取代主线，而是为‘低成本极简基线是否应继续占据搜索注意力’给出清晰结论。","summary":"执行一个 matched architecture probe：将主线切到 topk，其余 recipe 保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。该架构的最终重构是单一静态字典库上的有限稀疏加权和，属直接兼容；本轮只回答一个问题，即最简单的 LUTurbo 直接兼容单库方案是否仍值得继续保留。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0198.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_gated_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i；其中 low-rank trunk 项 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库上的加权和，residual 分支 Σ_i alpha_i b_i 可导出为静态 residual 字典上的稀疏加权和。gated selector 只改变在线选择与系数调制路径，不改变 decoder 端的有限加权和形式，因此能够导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性为扩展兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，lowrank_gated_residual 是否能在仍满足选择成本预算的情况下，相比 plain lowrank_residual 提供更好的 FVU；若它仍明显落后于 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 与主线，则说明 gate 作为 residual-side selector 改造在当前低 EF regime 下不值得继续。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 lowrank_gated_residual 仍明显劣于 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，则下一轮回到主线，只调一个成本轴如 TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或 STAGE1_RATIO。","若它仅小幅优于 lowrank_residual 但训练更慢或选择成本更高，则将 gating 视为负面信号，不再继续占用 probe 轮次。","继续避免 routed 与 bucketed matched probe，因为它们在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 超过 1.5×h×n 预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","lowrank_gated_residual 的导出路径仍是 trunk 静态库 + residual 静态字典库的有限加权和，属扩展兼容。","r193-r197 已基本排空 plain/factorized/direct-compatible 低成本路线；本轮补测 gated residual，判断 gating 是否只在强 soft-codebook backbone 上才可能有价值。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这是一个严格单变量的 matched probe，问题明确且与前几轮不重复：验证 residual 家族中的 gating 是否值得保留。它不改变最终部署公式，只隔离 selector 机制本身的贡献，适合在当前 probe 阶段为 residual-side 改造补全证据。","summary":"执行一个 matched architecture probe：将主线切到 lowrank_gated_residual，其余 recipe 保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。该架构的最终重构仍是 trunk 静态库与 residual 静态字典库上的有限加权和，属扩展兼容；本轮只回答一个问题，即 residual-side gating 是否足以让该 family 继续作为 LUTurbo 兼容候选。","touched_files":[]}

